"Что поделать, дело серьезное. Блюстителей, считай, опозорили публично, вот они и выслуживаются".
"Not much we can do, is there? This is serious. They've been publicly shamed, so now they're doing all they can to crawl back into the higher-ups' good graces."

languages.text: « C'est comme ça, on n'y peut rien. Et ce n'est encore qu'un début. Ils ont été humiliés publiquement, et maintenant, ils font tout ce qu'ils peuvent pour rentrer dans les bonnes grâces de la hiérarchie. »

languages.text: «No podemos hacerle nada, ¿no? Esto es grave. Han quedado deshonrados en público, y ahora tienen que hacer lo que sea para recuperar la confianza de las altas esferas».
languages.original_text: "Not much we can do, is there? This is serious. They've been publicly shamed, so now they're doing all they can to crawl back into the higher-ups' good graces."

languages.text: “不过我们又能怎么样呢？这件事闹得很大。他们被人当众打脸，所以他们打算尽一切手段，重新赢得高层的好感。”
languages.original_text: "Not much we can do, is there? This is serious. They've been publicly shamed, so now they're doing all they can to crawl back into the higher-ups' good graces."

traits.locale_text: “不过我们又能怎么样呢？这件事闹得很大。他们被人当众打脸，所以他们打算尽一切手段，重新赢得高层的好感。”

languages.text: 「私たちに出来ることは、あまりないだろう？これは深刻なんだ。公の場で恥をかかされた彼らは今、上層部のご機嫌を取るために全力を尽くしているんだ」
languages.original_text: "Not much we can do, is there? This is serious. They've been publicly shamed, so now they're doing all they can to crawl back into the higher-ups' good graces."

languages.text: "Wir können nicht viel tun, oder? Das ist eine ernste Sache. Sie wurden öffentlich bloßgestellt, darum tun sie nun alles, um wieder in die Gunst der Oberen zu kriechen."

languages.text: "Elimizden gelen çok da bir şey yok, değil mi? Bu iş ciddi. Herkesin içinde aşağılandılar. Şimdi de üstlerinin gözüne yeniden girebilmek için ellerinden geleni yapıyorlar."
